// Checklist
// Trackable task list with top-level items and optional sub-items, required items, and a progress bar.
// Items can be expanded to show sub-items, and each level can be checked independently.

FUNCTION toggleItem(itemId)
  Flips the checked state of a top-level item.
  Calls onChange with the updated item list.

---

FUNCTION toggleSubItem(itemId, subItemId)
  Flips the checked state of a sub-item within a top-level item.
  Calls onChange with the updated item list.

---

FUNCTION toggleExpand(itemId)
  Expands or collapses the sub-items for a top-level item.

---

FUNCTION Checklist(props) -> ReactNode                                    EXPORT
  Renders a list of checklist items with checkboxes and labels.
  Items with sub-items show an expand/collapse toggle.
  Required items are marked and cannot be skipped.
  Renders a progress bar showing checked items / total items.
